1
00:01:30,770 --> 00:01:35,039
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,390 --> 00:01:38,880
[2025] [Shengcheng Jinxing Co., Ltd]

3
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,710
Ms. Xia.

4
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,039
Sorry to keep you waiting.

5
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,420
It's okay. I just got here.

6
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:46,840
Please sit.

7
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,200
Okay.

8
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:48,940
Give me.

9
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,150
As for the contract,

10
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:52,640
