13
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:55,190
All right.

14
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,430
It's printed exactly according to

15
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,039
the version we previously

16
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,120
agreed upon.

17
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,770
There won't be any issues.

18
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,950
It's the end of the month today,

19
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,680
and also the end of the quarter.

20
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,030
If we wrap things up quickly,

21
00:02:11,030 --> 00:02:12,560
this payment can still count towards

22
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,590
