23
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:14,190
Am I right?

24
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:17,520
The business terms are fine.

25
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:20,079
The 8 major clauses of the contract,

26
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,140
totaling 13 pages, are also fine.

27
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:23,150
No issues here.

28
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:23,800
Then,

29
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,210
thank you, Mr. Jia.

30
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,590
If one lives to 70,

31
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,400
their lifetime consists of about

32
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,600
2.2 billion seconds.

33
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,800
We can never predict

34
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,310
