35
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,120
will be

36
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:38,120
life-changing.

37
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,120
Here's to a successful cooperation.

38
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,650
Alright.

39
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,800
I won't see you out then.

40
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,460
No problem.

41
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,680
Ms. Xia.

42
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,640
What's wrong?

43
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,370
Nothing.

44
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,030
My eyelid keeps twitching lately.

45
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,360
It makes me feel uneasy.

46
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:56,890
Let's go.

47
00:03:01,230 --> 00:03:04,810
[Episode 32]
[The Life-Changing Moment]

48
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,650
Xiaolan.

49
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,430
It's time.

50
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,160
Let's go.

51
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:47,770
Your dream is right ahead.

52
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:52,160
It's waiting for me ahead.

53
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,430
It's quite large-scale, isn't it?

54
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:08,750
Yeah. Thanks to you,

55
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,430
Mr. Mao.

56
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,710
Xiaolan deserves most of the credit.

57
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,240
The credit is mainly yours.

58
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:15,870
Hurry up, you two.

59
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:16,800
Put them here.

60
00:04:18,050 --> 00:04:18,870
Place them properly.

61
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:20,040
Make sure everything over there
is checked.

62
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,600
Quick, get these displayed.

63
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,930
Or we'll run out of time.

64
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,510
Hello, Chairman Du.

65
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,680
Is Xia Xiaolan not here yet?

66
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,360
Not yet.

67
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,510
Manager Ge.

68
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,620
When will Xiaolan be here?

69
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,870
And by the way, about last night—

70
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:31,730
