71
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:32,570
Yest...

72
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:33,040
Let's wait a bit longe...

73
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,700
She's here.

74
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:35,750
Mom.

75
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,240
Xiaolan.

76
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,240
-We've been waiting for you.
-Mr. Mao.

77
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:37,700
Auntie.

78
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,070
It's about time.

79
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:40,920
Ge Jian.

80
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,070
Let's get started.

81
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:42,930
Got it, Ms. Xia.

82
00:04:47,380 --> 00:04:50,060
[Golden Sands Pool—Qi Hang Property]

83
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,240
Welcome to

84
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,600
Golden Sands Pool.

85
00:05:46,870 --> 00:05:47,680
Congratulations, Mr. Xia,

86
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,630
