in Golden Sands Pool.

87
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,600
Crack the golden egg,

88
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,060
and good luck will follow.

89
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,280
Please watch the steps.

90
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:07,010
This way.

91
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:09,270
This is the reception room.

92
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,830
And this is the Western-style dining room.

93
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,600
The prices we quote are for

94
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:14,560
standard delivery units
with no interior decoration included.

95
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,000
Okay.

96
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,660
Hello, Sir.

97
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:17,400
Pardon me,

98
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:19,230
but smoking is prohibited here.

99
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:33,930
Golden Sands Pool?

100
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,630
The one with apartments going for

101
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:36,230
2,000 yuan per square meter.

102
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:38,970
They even throw in household registration.

103
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,480
Dajun.

104
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,690
Isn't that Young Master Du?

105
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,190
Do you want to go...

106
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:45,920
It's not him.

107
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,720
You must've seen wrong.

108
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:57,400
Add it in.

109
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:57,930
Okay.

110
00:06:57,950 --> 00:06:58,480
Alright.

111
00:06:58,870 --> 00:06:59,400
Xiaolan.

112
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,860
There's a call for you.

113
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:03,950
Hello?

114
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,150
Luo Yaozong is awake?

115
00:07:07,980 --> 00:07:09,630
It's not that we won't let you in.

116
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:11,090
This involves a homicide.

117
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,190
We have to wait for the police

118
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:13,000
to arrive.

119
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,680
Why wait for the police?

120
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,720
My son is lying in there!

121
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:16,230
Why can't I go in to see my son?

122
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:16,830
What are you doing...

123
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:17,430
She's right.

124
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:17,800
Chief Luo.

125
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,330
Since my grandson is awake,

126
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,920
I have the right to see him.

127
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,830
She's right.

128
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:24,160
Now that Luo Yaozong is awake,

129
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,920
we need to conduct

130
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,250
a routine questioning.

131
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,630
Hello. How is he doing?

132
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:31,720
Can he be questioned?

133
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:33,430
The patient's injuries are quite severe.

134
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:34,800
Although he's currently awake,

135
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,360
it's not advisable to engage him in
much conversation.

136
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,090
Understood.

137
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,390
We'll just ask him a few key questions.

138
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:39,830
Okay.

139
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,680
He's awake?

140
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,020
That...

141
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,120
That Xia Xiaolan

142
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,390
is just too lucky.

143
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,040
Yixiong,

144
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:49,920
calm down.

145
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:52,920
Yixiong,

146
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:53,720
don't worry.

147
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:55,560
I had Mosquito from Kong Island

148
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:56,680
handle this.

149
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:57,920
I had made everything

150
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,720
clear to them.

151
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,830
There's no way
they can trace it back to us.

152
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,680
You... I...

153
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,000
For such a big deal,

154
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,560
you had someone

155
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,420
fresh from Kong Island handle it?

156
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,430
It's not like that.

157
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,000
Yixiong.

158
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,120
You know,

159
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,360
since Liu

160
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,270
was reported by Bai Zhenzhu
and got taken in,

161
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,310
the police have been watching

162
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:17,430
our men too closely.

163
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:18,430
We're really short-handed...

164
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,430
Shut up!

165
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:20,510
Get out!

166
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,830
You can't even handle such a small task.

167
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,680
I'll smack you!

168
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:49,870
I need to go to Kong Island.

169
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:51,000
As soon as possible.

170
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:52,240
Luo Yaozong.

171
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,670
Do you remember

172
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:55,000
how you fell last night?

173
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:01,800
Let's go.

174
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:03,750
Move.

175
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:09,720
Move.

176
00:09:13,350 --> 00:09:14,810
Falling from this height,

177
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,700
he's definitely done for.

178
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,240
Where am I?

179
00:09:18,910 --> 00:09:20,080
It's so cold.

180
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:23,980
We're taking you somewhere else
for another round.

181
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:25,750
Buddy.

182
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,680
Don't blame me for not helping you.

183
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,360
When you get to the other side,

184
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,150
I'll burn you plenty of joss paper.

185
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:32,980
I drank too much...

186
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:33,440
Come on.

187
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:34,850
What are you doing?

188
00:09:38,650 --> 00:09:39,510
So,

189
00:09:39,510 --> 00:09:40,840
the last people you saw were

190
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,240
Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao?

191
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:45,510
And then?

192
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,940
You were drunk,

193
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,390
so you didn't know anything.

194
00:09:50,850 --> 00:09:52,060
When you woke up,

195
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,920
you were already on the roof.

196
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:56,030
It was Zhang Bing who pushed you off,

197
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:56,840
right?

198
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:01,960
Given his condition,

199
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:02,720
we won't be able to

200
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,320
get more details out of him anytime soon.

201
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,650
Let's call it a day then.

202
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,440
Let's step outside.

203
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,030
Yaozong.

204
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:09,320
Focus on recovering.

205
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,120
I won't let that bastard
who pushed you off

206
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,120
get away with it.

207
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,320
Officers.

208
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,530
You must catch the culprit.

209
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:20,290
He's the only heir left

210
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,480
of our Luo family.

211
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:25,440
My grandson's a victim.

212
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,710
Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao are murderers.

213
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,060
They must be executed!

214
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:30,950
That's right.

215
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,030
Sir,

216
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,530
sentencing isn't up to the police.

217
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,960
But this case

218
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,690
has indeed been reclassified.

219
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,000
I'll head back to the station right now

220
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,960
to re-interrogate those two

221
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,350
who pretended to steal steel,

222
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:43,320
and arrest Zhang Bing and Zhang Tao
as soon as possible.

223
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,550
Whatever you need from us,

224
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,720
we're ready to assist in any way.

225
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,120
Okay.

226
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,270
Yaozong.

227
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,910
If you remember anything,

228
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,370
be sure to tell the police.

229
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:58,200
Ms. Xia,

230
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,910
I'll head back to the station first.

231
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:01,320
Officer Zhou will take over from now

232
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,150
and follow up on the rest.

233
00:11:02,150 --> 00:11:03,030
Okay, thank you.

234
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:03,960
Okay, thank you.

235
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,330
Well...

236
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,480
Mr. Luo.

237
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:08,910
It wasn't easy

238
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:10,750
for your precious grandson to survive.

239
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,750
Don't start
getting any crooked ideas again

240
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,150
just because he's awake.

241
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,530
You heard it too.

242
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:16,480
The doctor said

243
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,340
his condition is still critical.

244
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,820
And all his medical bills

245
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,480
are being paid by Ms. Xia.

246
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,880
You guys should stay with him
for a couple more days.

247
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,080
He needs company now.

248
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,790
You heard it too—

249
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,840
he was pushed off by someone,

250
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:34,150
and that person still hasn’t been found.

251
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:35,550
If they find out

252
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:37,270
that Luo Yaozong isn't dead,

253
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,430
I'm afraid...

254
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,600
Then... Then...

255
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:40,480
Dad. Dad.

256
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,390
The most important thing right now

257
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,720
is that Yaozong is okay.

258
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,170
Then...

259
00:11:44,170 --> 00:11:45,230
Alright, alright.

260
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:45,920
Let's go.

261
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:46,680
Let's go.

262
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:10,600
Forty-seven units—

263
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,670
a total of 7,892,300 yuan!

264
00:12:13,050 --> 00:12:17,160
♪ I'm not willing to be ordinary ♪

265
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:18,120
Forty-seven units sold on the first day.

266
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,080
Only 4 buyers

267
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:20,710
♪ Sometimes I also want to
go a little crazy ♪

268
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,270
chose mortgage financing;

269
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,360
the other 43 buyers

270
00:12:21,270 --> 00:12:24,230
♪ Once I've decided, I'll be brave ♪

271
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,670
all chose to pay in full

272
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:23,870
within 3 days.

273
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:24,910
This way,

274
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:27,530
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

275
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,960
we'll be able to pay off

276
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,760
the first batch of the bank loan.

277
00:12:28,630 --> 00:12:30,200
Now that we can pay off half of the loan
in one go,

278
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,940
♪ There are laughter and tears ♪

279
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,510
with over 90 units left,

280
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,910
we'll make over 8 million!

281
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:34,820
♪ There's joy and sorrow ♪

282
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,320
Xiaolan.

283
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:38,150
♪ But this is life ♪

284
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:37,120
You've worked hard for so many years—

285
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:38,270
isn't this the day
you've been waiting for?

286
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:38,790
Yeah.

287
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:40,550
Congrats. Congrats.

288
00:12:40,130 --> 00:12:43,760
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

289
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:41,680
You finally made it!

290
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:42,960
Congrats, Xiaolan!

291
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:43,780
Congrats, Xiaolan.

292
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:47,080
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

293
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,600
Congratulations!

294
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:50,010
♪ We never give up ♪

295
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:53,960
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

296
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:57,200
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

297
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:57,720
Victory, invincible, long live—

298
00:12:57,230 --> 00:13:00,450
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

299
00:12:58,750 --> 00:12:59,750
none of these words

300
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:00,630
are enough to describe

301
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:01,790
how I feel right now.

302
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:03,760
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

303
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:03,870
A dream

304
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:05,000
I've had over and over,

305
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:07,000
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

306
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:07,510
a breath I've held back for so long,

307
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:13,900
♪ That'd be enough ♪

308
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:09,750
and desires once buried

309
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:11,790
beneath the trivialities of my past life—

310
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,590
all of it was waiting to burst out

311
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,090
in this very moment.

312
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,920
Great work today, everyone!

313
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,670
Ge Jian,

314
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,170
get everyone together.

315
00:13:24,170 --> 00:13:27,390
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

316
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,870
San's Food Stall tonight—

317
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:26,870
dinner's on me!

318
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:27,910
Great!

319
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:30,640
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

320
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:29,440
Thanks, Xiaolan!

321
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:31,390
Let's go!

322
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:33,950
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

323
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,010
Let's go!

324
00:13:34,330 --> 00:13:37,190
♪ As long as we do our best ♪

325
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:35,390
So happy.

326
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,270
Xiaolan.

327
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,840
You young people go celebrate.

328
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:44,090
♪ That'd be enough ♪

329
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,770
I won't join you.

330
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,160
I'm meeting a friend.

331
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,200
Mr. Mao.

332
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:42,330
Please sit.

333
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:45,910
Mr. Mao.

334
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:47,720
Thank you.

335
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,630
Golden Sands Pool is the first project

336
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,550
I designed independently after graduation.

337
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:53,610
Without your help,

338
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,440
I wouldn't be who I am today.

339
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:56,870
Enough with

340
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:57,960
the pleasantries.

341
00:13:58,410 --> 00:13:59,720
After the celebration,

342
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,480
get back to the office right away.

343
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:04,320
There are a whole bunch of issues
from the project process

344
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,920
I need to go through with you.

345
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,120
Yes, sure.

346
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,750
I still have much to learn,

347
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:10,150
and I need your guidance.

348
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,000
Mr. Mao.

349
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:19,440
Here.

350
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,420
This...

351
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:24,630
What,

352
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:27,270
are you giving me a house?

353
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:29,910
I've been paid

354
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,320
my full salary and bonuses.

355
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,150
I can't accept this.

356
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:33,350
Don't pull this on me.

357
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,680
I'm not accepting it.

358
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,270
Mr. Mao.

359
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:38,350
I know you're a stubborn old man.

360
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,840
But don't forget—

361
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:41,290
I'm a stubborn girl too.

362
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,750
Whatever I want to do,

363
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:43,750
I will get it done.

364
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:44,670
Just take this

365
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,390
as a token of respect

366
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:47,000
from a student to her teacher.

367
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
Please accept it.

368
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:55,910
Alright then, thank you.

369
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,040
Thank you.

370
00:14:59,000 --> 00:14:59,750
Mr. Mao.

371
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,240
This time,

372
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,080
don't give your nice apartment away

373
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,410
to your children again.

374
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,510
You've worked hard your whole life.

375
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:08,510
It's time for you to enjoy yourself.

376
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:10,360
If your children want a nice apartment,

377
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,160
let them work for it themselves.

378
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:13,750
Okay. Okay.

379
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,400
Girl, I'll listen to you.

380
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,870
Let's have a drink together!

381
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,330
Come on!

382
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,240
-To Ms. Xia!
-Ms. Xia!

383
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:25,770
Alright.

384
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,820
I'll save the pleasantries then.

385
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:29,120
Bottoms up!

386
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,390
Everyone, eat and drink

387
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:36,960
to your heart's content tonight.

388
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:39,080
We've still got a tough battle
to fight tomorrow.

389
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,850
Once we finish selling all the apartments,

390
00:15:40,850 --> 00:15:42,790
I'll take you all on
a team-building outing.

391
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:43,550
Team building?

392
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,080
Team building?

393
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:44,600
Ms. Xia,

394
00:15:44,910 --> 00:15:46,170
what is team building?

395
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,080
Team building

396
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,750
means taking all of you

397
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:49,600
out for fun together!

398
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,030
How about a trip to
Singapore, Malaysia, and Thailand?

399
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:51,910
Great!

400
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:53,120
Singapore, Malaysia, and Thailand!

401
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:53,750
Ms. Xia.

402
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:55,630
That tour route is super popular
right now.

403
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:56,870
I really want to go!

404
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:57,930
We'll definitely work hard.

405
00:15:57,930 --> 00:15:58,360
When the time comes,

406
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:59,440
you just go and have fun
with peace of mind.

407
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,300
I'll take care of your mom for you.

408
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:03,030
You'd better focus on
doing your job well first.

409
00:16:03,030 --> 00:16:04,960
The upcoming sales are just as important.

410
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,890
Li, you've got the right attitude.

411
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,280
Our food's coming up.

412
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,030
Come on.

413
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,330
A substantial dish.

414
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,600
Come on. Come on.

415
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,030
Here.

416
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:18,320
Alright.

417
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:20,630
This dish

418
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,750
is on me.

419
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,780
Wishing you soaring ambition

420
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,000
and victory from the start!

421
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,550
-Well said!
-Well said!

422
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,870
-Thank you, San.
-Thank you.

423
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,670
San,

424
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:29,600
every time we come here,

425
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,750
you give us discounts and free dishes.

426
00:16:30,750 --> 00:16:32,320
We almost feel embarrassed to come again.

427
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:34,080
We are also generating revenue for San
by coming here, right?

428
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,600
Everyone is welcome!

429
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,480
Come often!

430
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,440
Yes, right.

431
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:39,160
Xiaolan.

432
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,050
Look, your apartments

433
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,890
sell for 7 to 8 million,

434
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,630
while all these tables added together

435
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:46,910
won't make more than 700 yuan.

436
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:47,550
When you have time

437
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:48,200
from your busy schedule,

438
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,530
give me some advice too.

439
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:51,200
I'm not asking for huge wealth or fame.

440
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,440
I just want to take the top spot

441
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,570
on this food street.

442
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:57,210
Otherwise, I'd feel
I don't deserve Ms. Bai.

443
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,630
I heard that.

444
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:02,220
Don't talk nonsense.

445
00:17:02,330 --> 00:17:02,960
I think the way you are now

446
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,910
is good enough.

447
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:06,200
San.

448
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,849
Did someone just

449
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:10,000
call you,

450
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,530
asking for food delivery?

451
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,550
To be honest,

452
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,920
a while back, a regular customer of mine

453
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,050
sprained his ankle.

454
00:17:16,230 --> 00:17:17,109
He couldn't come here,

455
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:18,000
but he was craving our food.

456
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,000
He really wanted to eat it,

457
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,589
so I delivered it to him a few times.

458
00:17:20,589 --> 00:17:22,640
Now he wants me to deliver every day,

459
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:25,270
and others found out
and want delivery too.

460
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:25,790
Sure,

461
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,510
delivery is convenient for them.

462
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,200
But for me,

463
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,860
I'm just too busy to handle it.

464
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,720
Now I'm thinking,

465
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:32,450
I shouldn't have started this.

466
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:33,750
I think

467
00:17:33,750 --> 00:17:35,160
it's a great start.

468
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,220
Think about it—

469
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:38,310
where there's demand, there's a market.

470
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:38,880
San,

471
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:41,590
you could start a takeout service—

472
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:45,760
that is, a food delivery business.

473
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:46,960
Here's what you do:

474
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:49,020
set up a dedicated line for ordering,

475
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:50,440
and then hire a few people

476
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:52,200
just to deliver the food.

477
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,110
Then I'd have to hire more people.

478
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,400
Hiring is not a problem.

479
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,880
Zhenzhu's got several senior brothers

480
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,070
still doing part-time jobs out there.

481
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:01,920
That's right.

482
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,920
I'm short

483
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,720
on everything else,

484
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,720
but not manpower.

485
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:05,370
Right.

486
00:18:05,370 --> 00:18:06,680
Besides hiring people,

487
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:08,720
you also need to buy a few motorcycles.

488
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,240
You can set a delivery range,

489
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:10,970
for example,

490
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:12,530
3 or 5 kilometers,

491
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,480
and promise a specific delivery time.

492
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:15,000
This way,

493
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,350
the food delivered is both warm

494
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,160
and fresh.

495
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,830
If customers feel safe and enjoy the food,

496
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,360
they'll promote it for you.

497
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,200
Will this work?

498
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,160
With all the people and motorcycles,

499
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:24,700
how much will the cost increase?

500
00:18:24,700 --> 00:18:25,640
Why wouldn't it work?

501
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,440
It also increases your customer base.

502
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,750
You can also charge

503
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,160
a delivery fee as appropriate.

504
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,000
Some people

505
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,400
just don't want to go out.

506
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:34,240
They'd rather spend a few extra yuan

507
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,110
just to get your

508
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,640
door-to-door service.

509
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:40,040
Will it work?

510
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:41,640
All these years,

511
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,070
the ideas Xiaolan came up with

512
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,160
have never failed.

513
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:44,640
Here.

514
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:46,270
Hurry up and toast Ms. Xia.

515
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:46,800
Alright.

516
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,000
I'll start tomorrow.

517
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:48,270
Okay.

518
00:18:48,270 --> 00:18:48,640
Come on.

519
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,480
Let's toast Ms. Xia together.

520
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:50,830
Let's all toast Ms. Xia!

521
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:51,920
Ms. Xia!

522
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:53,070
Cheers.

523
00:18:53,070 --> 00:18:53,880
-Ms. Xia.
-Ms. Xia.

524
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,410
Alright.

525
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,920
Thank you all for your hard work
during this time.

526
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,920
I hope Qi Hang

527
00:18:58,160 --> 00:19:00,070
can be where your dreams set sail!

528
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:01,070
Well said!

529
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:01,920
Thank you, Ms. Xia!

530
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:02,380
Cheers.

531
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,540
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

532
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:07,140
Hold her steady. Hold her.

533
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:08,270
Mom.

534
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:10,590
Promise we'll never be apart.

535
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,610
Never apart. Never.

536
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,310
We're leaving.

537
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,550
Go ahead. Be careful.

538
00:19:14,550 --> 00:19:15,550
Watch the road. Be careful.

539
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,510
Zhou Cheng, drive safely.

540
00:19:16,510 --> 00:19:17,440
Whose car is this?

541
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,200
It's yours. Your car.

542
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:19,830
Is it hybrid?

543
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,480
What hybrid?

544
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:21,160
Yes, it is...

545
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,240
Renewable energy!

546
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,680
Yes, yes. It is.

547
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,300
Easy now. Careful.

548
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:26,710
She's really wasted.

549
00:19:28,030 --> 00:19:29,310
Take her to Granny Yu's.

550
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:30,690
I'll give Granny Yu a call.

551
00:19:30,690 --> 00:19:31,720
Don't worry, Uncle, Mrs. Liu.

552
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,150
We're off.

553
00:19:32,150 --> 00:19:33,310
Sir, can we go now?

554
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:33,640
Yeah.

555
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:34,790
We can go. We're going.

556
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:35,750
Watch your hand.

557
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:36,750
We're off, Uncle.

558
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:37,400
Be careful.

559
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,200
Drive safely.

560
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:38,720
Okay.

561
00:19:40,270 --> 00:19:41,270
Take care.

562
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:03,720
Go inside.

563
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,110
You're making me stay in this dump?

564
00:20:16,110 --> 00:20:18,440
You're lucky to have a roof
over your head.

565
00:20:18,590 --> 00:20:20,590
At least you're out of the elements.

566
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,310
When will she see me?

567
00:20:23,720 --> 00:20:25,400
You didn't even handle things properly,

568
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:27,130
yet you act all high and mighty?

569
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:29,050
If you want to see Ms. Vivi,

570
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:30,960
you'll have to wait.

571
00:20:47,110 --> 00:20:47,960
Officer Liu called me

572
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:48,760
this morning.

573
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,640
Zhang Tao and Zhang Bing have been caught,

574
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,480
but neither of them has seen Ke Yixiong.

575
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:54,480
They said they were acting on orders

576
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:56,160
from someone called "Mosquito."

577
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,290
Another scapegoat.

578
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:59,200
Ke Yixiong got away again.

579
00:20:59,200 --> 00:20:59,750
That Ke Yixiong

580
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,350
is really running out of men.

581
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,110
This "Mosquito" guy
hadn't been with him for long.

582
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:05,110
He was supposed to disappear
once the job was done,

583
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,690
but he spent the money on whoring.

584
00:21:06,690 --> 00:21:08,000
After the police caught him,

585
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:09,930
he gave up Ke Yixiong immediately.

586
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,830
It's a pity

587
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,070
that Ke still managed to escape.

588
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:14,070
What a sly old fox.

589
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:16,230
Ke Yixiong

590
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:17,720
has a lot of cases hanging over him—

591
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,960
robbery, theft,

592
00:21:19,220 --> 00:21:20,420
smuggling, and such.

593
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:21,350
Longcheng has already

594
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:23,150
issued a warrant for his arrest.

595
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:25,160
As someone connected to him,

596
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:25,750
you might also need to

597
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:27,410
cooperate with questioning.

598
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,370
You're here.

599
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:30,520
Come on in.

600
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:31,510
Okay.

601
00:21:35,040 --> 00:21:37,540
[Golden Sands Pool]

602
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:05,830
This way, please.

603
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:07,570
Thanks for coming.

604
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,830
Please take a look at this apartment.

605
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:12,680
This is our model unit.

606
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,880
All of our model units

607
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:15,880
are handled by Yuanhui Decoration.

608
00:22:15,890 --> 00:22:16,950
You can take a look.

609
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,960
This here is one of the bedrooms,

610
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,830
and it's also decorated by Yuanhui.

611
00:22:25,830 --> 00:22:27,070
Check it out. It's very spacious

612
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:28,110
and comfortable.

613
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,310
Hello, Ma'am.

614
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:33,240
Why are these all marked?

615
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:35,070
Yes, they're all sold out.

616
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:35,830
Ma'am,

617
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:36,960
why don't you come back tomorrow

618
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:37,890
and check again?

619
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:38,680
Because tomorrow

620
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,160
is the payment deadline,

621
00:22:40,490 --> 00:22:41,590
and it's possible that

622
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:43,160
some people still won't have gathered

623
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:44,590
enough money by then.

624
00:22:44,950 --> 00:22:46,100
You might get lucky.

625
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,480
There's one left over there!

626
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,270
Ma'am,

627
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,970
please come back tomorrow.

628
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,640
Ma'am, I'll walk you out.

629
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:06,690
Xiaolan.

630
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:12,960
What?

631
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,160
Did you see that Luo Yaozong

632
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,160
has mostly recovered,

633
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:16,880
so you came to ask for medical fees?

634
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:17,830
You young lady,

635
00:23:18,520 --> 00:23:20,880
why do you always look down on people
like that?

636
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,470
Our Luo family

637
00:23:21,470 --> 00:23:22,860
has never been that low.

638
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:24,830
These past few days at the hospital,

639
00:23:24,830 --> 00:23:25,550
I've seen

640
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,960
that you've been genuinely

641
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:29,440
spending money and effort,
trying to save my grandson.

642
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:30,790
I'm not the kind of person

643
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:32,120
who likes owing favors.

644
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,510
I came today

645
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,480
because there's something

646
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:36,940
I'd like to confess to you.

647
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:38,830
So,

648
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,440
you guys really were plotting against me

649
00:23:40,440 --> 00:23:41,300
behind my back.

650
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,440
Forget it, forget it.

651
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:44,700
I won't argue with you.

652
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,830
Back then, when we went to cause trouble
at Golden Sands Pool—

653
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:50,110
including having my grandson
work there as a security guard—

654
00:23:50,110 --> 00:23:52,030
someone paid us to do it.

655
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,030
And

656
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:56,310
that old matter from over 20 years ago—

657
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,160
someone also had me

658
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,960
deliberately tell you about it.

659
00:24:01,310 --> 00:24:02,310
Okay, I got it.

660
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:03,920
Thank you, Chief Luo.

661
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:04,920
You may leave now.

662
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:05,680
So...

663
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:08,110
So, are we even now?

664
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:11,270
Even?

665
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:13,790
Wait.

666
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,160
You plotted against me,

667
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,840
yet I spent money saving your grandson,

668
00:24:17,840 --> 00:24:19,900
and now you're telling me we're even?

669
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:23,350
Forget it.

670
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,750
If you say we're even, then we're even.

671
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:26,350
Go on home.

672
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:28,790
Thanks, then.

673
00:24:34,110 --> 00:24:35,510
Who do you think

674
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,310
leaked Xu Zhongyi's info to you?

675
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,460
At first, I suspected it was Xia Ziyu.

676
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,310
After all, her reach

677
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:41,880
extends all the way to Nie Weiguo.

678
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:42,790
She even manipulated

679
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:44,750
the design-drawing plagiarism incident.

680
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:46,350
But later I thought about it—

681
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:48,750
apart from you and my mom,

682
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,920
no one else knows about Granny Yu.

683
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:51,960
So there must be someone else

684
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:52,760
in the middle—

685
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:54,350
someone who's been sharing information

686
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:55,160
with Xia Ziyu.

687
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:57,620
Du Zhaohui?

688
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:00,170
It can't be him.

689
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:03,920
Anyway, we'll find out eventually.

690
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:04,520
By the way,

691
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,180
Jiang Yan told me today

692
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:08,570
that Liu Tianquan had been arrested
in Shengcheng.

693
00:25:08,570 --> 00:25:10,170
He wouldn't be stupid enough

694
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,630
to still dare come to Shengcheng
at a time like this, right?

695
00:25:12,630 --> 00:25:13,760
I guess Chairman Du

696
00:25:13,790 --> 00:25:15,320
sent him here to surrender.

697
00:25:15,830 --> 00:25:16,680
Anyway,

698
00:25:17,470 --> 00:25:18,380
Shi Kai's case

699
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:20,410
has finally come to a conclusion.

700
00:25:25,070 --> 00:25:26,130
Prosecutor Liang.

701
00:25:28,750 --> 00:25:29,350
Wu Hao.

702
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:30,920
Regarding this case,

703
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,110
your Zhiyuan Law Firm

704
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:33,240
really helped a lot.

705
00:25:33,510 --> 00:25:34,960
Whether for public duty
or personal reasons,

706
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,090
we must do our utmost

707
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:37,550
in Liu Tianquan's case.

708
00:25:37,750 --> 00:25:38,950
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

709
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:48,260
[Shengcheng People's Court]

710
00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:45,510
Your Honor,

711
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:46,790
members of the panel,

712
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,560
today, as the public prosecutor,

713
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:50,240
I bring charges against the defendant
in this case,

714
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,040
Liu Tianquan.

715
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:52,720
Shi Kai.

716
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:55,110
We've finally reached this day.

717
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:57,830
Liu Tianquan has been arrested,

718
00:25:58,110 --> 00:25:59,270
and Xiao Jianyong has testified

719
00:25:59,270 --> 00:26:00,730
to Liu Tianquan's crimes.

720
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,580
For the truth and for justice,

721
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:06,210
you gave your passion,

722
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:08,130
and even your life.

723
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:11,330
Justice prevails.

724
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,620
Those who have scorned the law

725
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:16,830
are about to face its judgment.

726
00:26:19,580 --> 00:26:25,540
[Sell One, Donate One Yuan]

727
00:26:22,070 --> 00:26:23,640
Please welcome Mr. Wu Qiang

728
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:25,840
to present the award for Luna Clothing!

729
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:29,110
Congrats. Congrats.

730
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,310
Thank you. Thank you.

731
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:30,720
Here.

732
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:31,160
Okay.

733
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,000
Keep up the good work.

734
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:32,720
I will.

735
00:26:36,260 --> 00:26:37,500
Time flies.

736
00:26:38,350 --> 00:26:39,720
Everyone in Shengcheng

737
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:41,440
is growing rapidly

738
00:26:41,790 --> 00:26:43,110
along with this city.

739
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:05,450
Everyone is striding forward.

740
00:27:06,150 --> 00:27:07,950
But I, who never stopped moving,

741
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,320
seem to have slowed down.

742
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:13,540
[Qi Hang Property Co., Ltd]

743
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:13,200
Ms. Xia,

744
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:14,960
we are all curious about

745
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,360
what your next plans are.

746
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,530
I heard several Kong Island investors

747
00:27:18,530 --> 00:27:19,920
are coming to Shengcheng
to build properties.

748
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:20,350
Yes.

749
00:27:21,030 --> 00:27:22,590
Kong Island investors
are both wealthy and capable,

750
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,110
so they'll definitely go for
large-scale developments.

751
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:24,750
There's no need for us

752
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,410
to go head-to-head with them.

753
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:28,400
For now, just finish

754
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,600
the work at hand well.

755
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:30,960
When a big project

756
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,220
is finally confirmed,

757
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,720
I hope each of you

758
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:35,240
will be more mature than you are now

759
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:37,500
and more capable of standing on your own.

760
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:39,030
Rest assured, everyone.

761
00:27:39,030 --> 00:27:40,480
Since Qi Hang has set sail,

762
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,480
it won't stop.

763
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,930
It's starting. It's starting.

764
00:27:57,270 --> 00:27:57,800
Xiaolan.

765
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,480
Xia Xiaolan.

766
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:00,510
That custom drama you guys made—

767
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:02,270
my grandma loves it so much.

768
00:28:02,270 --> 00:28:03,270
Every time, she asks me

769
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:04,790
whether that character Cui

770
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:06,210
was written based on me.

771
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:07,960
She's been going around
telling all the neighbors about it.

772
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,360
How's my scriptwriting?

773
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:09,790
It's great.

774
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:10,720
The characters in it

775
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:12,180
do have traces of you guys,

776
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:13,830
but for television purposes,

777
00:28:13,830 --> 00:28:15,880
they've been exaggerated and reshaped.

778
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:16,750
The ratings for this show

779
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:17,680
are pretty good,

780
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,200
and sales in the store have also gone up.

781
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:19,750
Yeah.

782
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:20,270
That's right.

783
00:28:20,270 --> 00:28:21,800
Leading the fashion trend.

784
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:24,950
I really envy you, Chen.

785
00:28:25,510 --> 00:28:27,110
When are you going to be a dad?

786
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,090
Soon. Very soon.

787
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:33,400
We are your fans.

788
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,160
Can we get an autograph?

789
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:34,830
One by one.

790
00:28:35,310 --> 00:28:36,960
Thank you. Thank you.

791
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,560
Do you know how hard this is?

792
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:42,350
Come on.

793
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:45,450
Be careful.

794
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:47,000
Here.

795
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,410
Good job.

796
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,680
Safety first. Keep it steady.

797
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:52,070
Be careful not to spill the soup.

798
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:52,510
Okay.

799
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:54,110
Be careful. Ride slowly.

800
00:28:54,110 --> 00:28:55,570
Ride slowly. Ride slowly.

801
00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:01,970
Your business is really booming now.

802
00:29:01,970 --> 00:29:02,920
It's only been a short while,

803
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:03,920
and there've been several delivery runs.

804
00:29:03,920 --> 00:29:04,790
Xiaolan is like

805
00:29:05,220 --> 00:29:07,410
the God of Wealth sent from heaven.

806
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,270
There's no idea of hers

807
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:09,830
that doesn't make money.

808
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:11,200
Xia.

809
00:29:11,400 --> 00:29:12,240
I'm also curious about

810
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,750
what your next plans are.

811
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:15,400
Is there anything I can join in on?

812
00:29:15,400 --> 00:29:16,230
Some say

813
00:29:16,230 --> 00:29:18,000
you're going to Qiong Island
to speculate on land,

814
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,030
some say

815
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:20,400
you're going to Kong Island
to trade stocks,

816
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,070
and others say

817
00:29:21,070 --> 00:29:22,440
you'll stay in Shengcheng

818
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,750
to do commercial real estate.

819
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:24,720
Which one is true?

820
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,440
Well, can't I take a break?

821
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,590
Do I have to keep spinning

822
00:29:27,590 --> 00:29:28,590
like a top?

823
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,880
Besides,

824
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:31,000
who said Qi Hang

825
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,730
doesn't have any new projects?

826
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:33,760
What project?

827
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:36,110
It's still in preparation.

828
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,000
No comment.

829
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,240
Alright, alright. I won't ask.

830
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:41,970
Look at this.

831
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:44,050
Everyone's coupled up.

832
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:46,030
These two

833
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:48,210
are about to have a baby—

834
00:29:48,270 --> 00:29:49,640
a happy family.

835
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,270
These two

836
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,400
are just a marriage certificate away.

837
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,240
And these two

838
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,880
are passionately in love.

839
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,680
I'm the only one left.

840
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,510
So unlucky in love.

841
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,640
Wei.

842
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,510
You are so bitter.

843
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:06,170
It's quite gross, you know?

844
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:07,830
Since you like her,

845
00:30:07,830 --> 00:30:09,240
why don't you just tell her?

846
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,790
You shower her with attention every day,

847
00:30:10,790 --> 00:30:12,050
but you won't confess.

848
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,000
Don't tell me you just want

849
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:14,130
to string her along.

850
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:15,170
Xiaolan said

851
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:17,270
people like that are called "scumbags."

852
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:17,800
Scumbag.

853
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:18,530
Scumbag.

854
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,240
Scumbag.

855
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:21,720
Don't talk nonsense.

856
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:23,110
I've wanted to confess for a long time.

857
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:24,640
I... I've even

858
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,070
rehearsed my lines so many times.

859
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,930
Ask Cheng if you don't believe me.

860
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:29,600
Right.

861
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,940
Every night in his dreams, he's like,

862
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:32,880
"Li..."

863
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:35,480
Alright, alright, that's enough.

864
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:36,960
No need to go into details.

865
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:37,640
No need?

866
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:38,270
No need, no need.

867
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:39,040
Wei.

868
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:39,550
I know it's because

869
00:30:39,550 --> 00:30:41,020
you're worried since Li is already
under a lot of pressure,

870
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:41,960
if you confess to her,

871
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,640
it'll only make her feel
even more pressured, right?

872
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,080
Look.

873
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:45,400
Xiaolan understands me best.

874
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,110
Soulmate.

875
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,720
Li's mother's situation
is still uncertain.

876
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,270
No one knows when she'll wake up.

877
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,160
But Li can't possibly

878
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,550
stay stuck where she is forever.

879
00:30:52,550 --> 00:30:53,160
One day she'll have to

880
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,270
move forward.

881
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:55,440
If you don't

882
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:56,680
make things clear now

883
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,030
and lose this chance,

884
00:30:58,030 --> 00:30:59,360
wouldn't that be a pity?

885
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,270
Alright, don't be so depressed.

886
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:05,270
Come on, let's have a drink.

887
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:05,750
Cheers.

888
00:31:06,560 --> 00:31:07,930
Then let's wish that Wei

889
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:08,960
won't be a scumbag.

890
00:31:08,960 --> 00:31:10,110
Hear, hear.

891
00:31:10,250 --> 00:31:10,790
To the scumbag.

892
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:11,920
Don't be a scumbag!

893
00:31:13,910 --> 00:31:21,990
[Luna's Story]

894
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:25,610
Got any new money-making plans

895
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:28,020
that you can't even tell me about?

896
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,270
I really haven't figured it out yet.

897
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:33,310
That's why I didn't say anything.

898
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:35,110
I'm not trying to be mysterious.

899
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:35,930
However,

900
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:37,790
I may not have a plan for making money,

901
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:39,750
I do have one for spending it.

902
00:31:42,350 --> 00:31:43,310
What do you think about

903
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,200
me setting up

904
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:46,740
a student aid program?

905
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,350
Would you also think

906
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:51,520
that I've only just made a little money

907
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:52,550
and I'm already getting ahead of myself,

908
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:54,010
trying to play the savior?

909
00:31:55,790 --> 00:31:57,450
It's because of You Li, right?

910
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:58,200
Besides,

911
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:00,230
even if you were a savior,

912
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:02,270
Darling, you'd definitely be

913
00:32:02,550 --> 00:32:04,680
a beautiful and kind-hearted savior.

914
00:32:09,350 --> 00:32:10,110
Zhou Cheng.

915
00:32:10,510 --> 00:32:11,400
You know what?

916
00:32:13,130 --> 00:32:14,410
In front of others,

917
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:15,770
I don't dare to be smug.

918
00:32:16,030 --> 00:32:17,290
But only in front of you

919
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:18,750
can I be like a child

920
00:32:18,750 --> 00:32:20,410
who got their favorite candy—

921
00:32:20,790 --> 00:32:21,880
carefree

922
00:32:22,070 --> 00:32:23,070
and carried away.

923
00:32:23,750 --> 00:32:24,950
That's because I know

924
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:26,650
you're not just happy

925
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:29,550
because you made money
from the Golden Sands Pool project.

926
00:32:29,550 --> 00:32:31,160
It's more about the whole process:

927
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:31,960
the planning,

928
00:32:32,350 --> 00:32:32,960
the moves,

929
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,400
and finally reaping the rewards—

930
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:35,860
the joy of the entire game.

931
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,000
You know,

932
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,410
you earned the money honestly,

933
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,310
so you should feel proud
and enjoy it to the fullest.

934
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:44,160
Life's too short not to savor
your victories, you know.

935
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:46,220
It was only then that I truly realized

936
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,400
that the ability to flaunt

937
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:50,000
or take pride in your success

938
00:32:50,310 --> 00:32:52,640
can be even more important
than success itself.

939
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,840
But this idea of yours

940
00:32:54,310 --> 00:32:55,550
doesn't just require money—

941
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:58,480
it also needs the cooperation of
the education authorities.

942
00:32:58,480 --> 00:32:59,920
Still, since you've decided to go for it,

943
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,120
let's make it happen.

944
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:03,310
Also,

945
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:03,930
maybe...

946
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:08,080
♪ Maybe all encounters in the world ♪

947
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,200
Also,

948
00:33:08,290 --> 00:33:12,570
♪ Are predetermined by destiny ♪

949
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:10,790
we should find a time

950
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,880
to go get our marriage certificate.

951
00:33:14,330 --> 00:33:19,290
♪ The opening and closing chapters
are written ♪

952
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:17,640
Okay.

953
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:23,330
♪ From when we first met ♪

954
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:27,830
♪ Till now, though much has changed ♪

955
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:34,980
♪ Our hearts remain unchanged ♪

956
00:33:35,730 --> 00:33:40,670
♪ Having a dream in your eyes ♪

957
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:50,840
♪ Time passes by,
yet I still love you the same ♪

958
00:33:51,490 --> 00:33:56,350
♪ After traveling through the crowds
and dark tides ♪

959
00:33:56,940 --> 00:34:06,100
♪ We must embrace
with the weight of the moment ♪

960
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,240
Is it you?

961
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,270
The voice that keeps

962
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,480
hovering in my mind?

963
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:07,500
Are you trying to remind me of something?

964
00:34:46,550 --> 00:34:47,679
You broke so easily.

965
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,330
Mr. Kang.

966
00:34:58,190 --> 00:34:58,810
Mr. Kang.

967
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:02,510
Li.

968
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:03,740
Li.

969
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,630
Kang, you're here again.

970
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:06,510
This young man

971
00:35:06,510 --> 00:35:07,370
is really nice.

972
00:35:08,330 --> 00:35:08,970
Ms. Wang.

973
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,110
He's my friend.

974
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:12,030
I've been around long enough.

975
00:35:12,030 --> 00:35:13,490
Don't you think I can tell?

976
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:14,360
It's just

977
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,510
if you two

978
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:16,770
don't make a move soon,

979
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,480
the other young folks here

980
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:20,050
won't be able to sit still.

981
00:35:23,960 --> 00:35:24,480
Li.

982
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,910
Don't listen to Ms. Wang.

983
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:28,950
Our conscience is clear.

984
00:35:29,070 --> 00:35:29,840
Friends are supposed to

985
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:31,200
help each other out, right?

986
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:32,200
Here, have a tangerine.

987
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:33,400
You're always the one helping me.

988
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:34,930
I haven't helped you at all.

989
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:36,480
Fine.

990
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,610
I'll be honest then.

991
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,800
My conscience isn't exactly clear.

992
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,760
So we're even.

993
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,800
What are you laughing at?

994
00:35:45,200 --> 00:35:46,710
You're not making any sense.

995
00:35:46,710 --> 00:35:48,170
How does that make us even?

996
00:35:50,440 --> 00:35:51,110
Li.

997
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,070
You know

998
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:53,920
how I feel.

999
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:56,110
Actually,

1000
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,280
it was only after

1001
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:59,230
learning about your family situation

1002
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:01,400
that I truly got to know you

1003
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:02,890
and understand you.

1004
00:36:03,710 --> 00:36:04,840
You're a good girl.

1005
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:07,550
I know all your energy right now

1006
00:36:07,550 --> 00:36:09,360
is focused on your mom's illness.

1007
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,880
You don't have the energy
to think about the future,

1008
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,190
and you don't dare to.

1009
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:17,250
Kang Wei...

1010
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:19,320
It's okay.

1011
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,610
I just want to say...

1012
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:21,960
Look,

1013
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,000
now that your boss

1014
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:23,880
is also my boss,

1015
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,570
we're sort of colleagues.

1016
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,510
We see each other every day.

1017
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,230
We still have plenty of time ahead.

1018
00:36:29,230 --> 00:36:29,880
Anyway,

1019
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,230
I'll wait for you.

1020
00:36:35,590 --> 00:36:36,190
Kang Wei.

1021
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,280
You're really nice to me,

1022
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,760
and I understand what you mean.

1023
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,190
But...

1024
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:48,000
Mom.

1025
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:50,030
Mom?

1026
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:51,840
Mom!

1027
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:53,360
Mom!

1028
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,280
You...

1029
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:55,440
Li.

1030
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:56,510
Her finger moved.

1031
00:36:56,510 --> 00:36:57,510
Her finger moved!

1032
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,960
Nurse! Doctor!

1033
00:36:59,110 --> 00:37:00,320
Can you hear me?

1034
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,070
It's Li, Mom.

1035
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:10,110
The patient's condition
has improved significantly,

1036
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,850
and she's regaining consciousness.

1037
00:37:11,850 --> 00:37:13,190
We'll keep observing her.

1038
00:37:13,190 --> 00:37:15,110
There's a good chance she'll wake up.

1039
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,510
Call me if anything happens.

1040
00:37:16,510 --> 00:37:17,170
Thank you, Doctor.

1041
00:37:17,170 --> 00:37:17,630
Thank you, Doctor.

1042
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,170
Thank you.

1043
00:37:18,170 --> 00:37:18,770
Thank you.

1044
00:37:20,590 --> 00:37:21,150
Mom.

1045
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:26,320
Don't worry.

1046
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,420
She'll get better.

1047
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:30,310
Thank you, everyone.

1048
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:32,840
Mom.

1049
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:58,510
Li.

1050
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:00,990
Cheng hired a caregiver.

1051
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,030
She'll come over this afternoon.

1052
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,070
You can try her out then.

1053
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,030
If she's good, keep her.

1054
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:04,550
If not,

1055
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:05,480
we'll hire someone else.

1056
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,630
Anyway, Xiaolan said

1057
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:07,320
we must find a suitable one

1058
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:08,250
for your mother.

1059
00:38:09,030 --> 00:38:09,840
Thank you all.

1060
00:38:10,810 --> 00:38:11,810
Don't mention it.

1061
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:13,710
Your mom is getting better day by day.

1062
00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:15,040
We're all happy for you.

1063
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,360
And I believe

1064
00:38:16,930 --> 00:38:17,680
that your mom

1065
00:38:17,710 --> 00:38:19,040
will definitely wake up

1066
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,770
and talk to you again someday.

1067
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:23,800
By the way, Li,

1068
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,490
if your mom wakes up,

1069
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,290
what do you plan to tell her?

1070
00:38:30,110 --> 00:38:31,360
I want to tell her

1071
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:33,240
what happened during this time.

1072
00:38:33,550 --> 00:38:34,550
I want to tell her

1073
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:36,070
I have a great job

1074
00:38:36,510 --> 00:38:38,310
and an amazing, wonderful boss.

1075
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,730
I also met a lot of good people.

1076
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:43,280
Although these days have been tiring,

1077
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:45,590
I feel happy every day,

1078
00:38:46,150 --> 00:38:46,760
and I feel that the future

1079
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:47,880
is full of hope.

1080
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,400
I hope Mom can be like me—

1081
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,400
let go of the past

1082
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:55,070
and look forward.

1083
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:57,840
Well said.

1084
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:00,100
Your mom will surely be happy.

1085
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:04,770
I also want to tell her one more thing.

1086
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:09,280
That I met a very good person.

1087
00:39:11,310 --> 00:39:13,140
Sometimes he's a bit clumsy,

1088
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,400
but sometimes he's a bit too quick-witted.

1089
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:17,710
He talks a lot,

1090
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,800
but he always means well.

1091
00:39:20,550 --> 00:39:21,680
He is enthusiastic,

1092
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,550
brave,

1093
00:39:22,710 --> 00:39:23,440
and kind.

1094
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:25,850
It may sound like

1095
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:27,710
nothing special,

1096
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:31,480
but in my heart,

1097
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:33,960
he's different from others.

1098
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:37,030
He has been by my side

1099
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:38,230
for a long, long time.

1100
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,480
Actually,

1101
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:44,490
I've wanted to tell him for a while

1102
00:39:45,630 --> 00:39:46,690
that I like him too.

1103
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:52,800
Li.

1104
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:55,090
So you're willing to be with me?

1105
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:58,320
Um...

1106
00:39:58,710 --> 00:39:59,190
Auntie,

1107
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:00,280
don't worry.

1108
00:40:00,510 --> 00:40:02,230
I'll always treat Li well.

1109
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:04,790
Please rest assured.

1110
00:40:10,590 --> 00:40:11,110
Mom.

1111
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:26,320
Hello, Ms. Xia.

1112
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:26,630
Morning.

1113
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:26,960
Good morning, Ms. Xia.

1114
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:27,230
Morning.

1115
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,090
Hello, Ms. Xia.

1116
00:40:48,870 --> 00:40:50,620
[The 6th International
Youth Architectural Design Festival]

1117
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:52,240
But I didn't sign up.

1118
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:01,230
Today is
the foundation acceptance inspection

1119
00:41:01,230 --> 00:41:03,760
for Phase II of
the Electronics City project.

1120
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,360
Why isn't Mr. Du here yet?

1121
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:06,360
What?

1122
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:08,190
Just because his status changed,

1123
00:41:08,190 --> 00:41:09,920
now he's ignoring the business

1124
00:41:10,120 --> 00:41:11,920
and doesn't care about
the groundwork anymore?

1125
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:12,710
It's not like that.

1126
00:41:12,710 --> 00:41:14,190
Mr. Mao, please don't be angry.

1127
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:14,720
You know?

1128
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:15,840
There really is a lot

1129
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,070
going on in Kong Island.

1130
00:41:17,070 --> 00:41:17,590
Right?

1131
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,070
So Young Master sent me

1132
00:41:19,070 --> 00:41:20,600
to come work in Shengcheng.

1133
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:22,360
Hello?

1134
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:23,840
Hello? Hua.

1135
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:25,440
Are you with Mr. Mao?

1136
00:41:25,670 --> 00:41:26,230
Yes, I am.

1137
00:41:27,110 --> 00:41:27,630
Mr. Mao.

1138
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,320
Who is it?

1139
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:30,440
It's Ms. Xia.

1140
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:32,800
Hello?

1141
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,510
Mr. Mao.

1142
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,320
I received

1143
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:38,000
an invitation letter from

1144
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,280
the World Architecture Construction Federation.

1145
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:41,110
It says my Xinghe Theater project

1146
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:42,370
has been shortlisted.

1147
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:43,650
Good.

1148
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:46,230
Though I had the right to
make recommendations,

1149
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,690
the shortlisted projects

1150
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:49,280
were decided by the judges

1151
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:51,000
collectively.

1152
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:55,710
Your work truly earned it on its own.

1153
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,000
I heard

1154
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,050
this year's ceremony will be held
on Kong Island.

1155
00:42:00,230 --> 00:42:02,070
You're finally making a name for yourself

1156
00:42:02,070 --> 00:42:03,840
on the international stage.

1157
00:42:04,510 --> 00:42:05,040
Alright.

1158
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:09,770
Hello? Hello? Ms. Xia?

1159
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,810
Congratulations, Ms. Xia.

1160
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:12,510
Hua.

1161
00:42:12,710 --> 00:42:14,080
I'm going to Kong Island in a few days.

1162
00:42:14,080 --> 00:42:15,030
Please help me make the arrangements.

1163
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,280
Okay, no problem.

1164
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:18,110
I'll call Young Master later

1165
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:20,030
and tell him to pick you up
at the checkpoint.

1166
00:42:20,030 --> 00:42:20,630
Thank you.

1167
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,100
Kong Island Peninsula Hotel.

1168
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:47,650
I haven't opened this for a long time.

1169
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,000
The strings of numbers here

1170
00:42:50,550 --> 00:42:51,480
are all from the despair I felt

1171
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:53,110
when my memory was in chaos.

1172
00:42:54,010 --> 00:42:54,960
Thank you, Zhou Cheng,

1173
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:56,150
for pulling me out

1174
00:42:56,150 --> 00:42:56,950
of this chaos.

1175
00:42:57,740 --> 00:43:00,100
I still find it hard to let go,

1176
00:43:01,150 --> 00:43:02,110
but I'm no longer afraid.
